('Three Kings Parade','Held in El Barrio (East Harlem), New York, the time-honored Parade begins at 106th St and Park Ave and ends at 115th St and Park Ave featuring camels, floats, and live music by BombaYo, Annette Aguilar & Stringbeans, Fogo Azul, and more. Soon after, we invite parade-goers to come back to El Museo del Barrio for a live musical performance in El Teatro from 1:30-3pm.', 'January 5, 2024', 'Manhattan', 'Parade', true, 'https://www.elmuseo.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Screenshot-2023-11-21-at-11.51.25-AM-1536x685.png', 'https://www.elmuseo.org/event/47th-annual-three-kings-day-parade/'),
