('The Winter Show', 'The Winter Show is the première art, antiques, and design fair in America, featuring many of the top experts in the fine and decorative arts. The 70th edition of The Winter Show will be held in the historic Park Avenue Armory where a breadth of works spanning 5,000 years will be presented by over 68 internationally renowned dealers.', 'January 19 - 28, 2024', 'Manhattan', 'Art Show', false,'https://images.thewintershow.org/wintershowmedia/slideshows/_T637746116327281790.png?height=700&width=1900&mode=crop&scale=both&format=jpg&qlt=90', 'https://www.thewintershow.org/'),
('NYC Boat Show', 'The boat show is finally here! The Discover Boating® New York Boat Show®, in partnership with Progressive Insurance®, is returning to the Javits Center January 24-28, 2024 As your premier destination for boats, boating accessories, and on-the-water adventures, the Discover Boating New York Boat Show has something in store for every boating enthusiast. And with hundreds of new boats on display, plus ample activities to explore, this iconic event is ideal for first-time boaters and seasoned pros alike.', 'January 24-28, 2024', 'Manhattan', 'Boat Show', false,'https://www.discoverboating.com/sites/default/files/NY-Boat-Show_0.png','https://www.nyboatshow.com/' ),
('Ice Skating', 'Ice skating in NYC is one of the city’s most beloved seasonal traditions. While some skating rinks are open year-round, ice skating in the winter — especially around the holidays — is a special treat that will warm your cockles with the spirit of the season. The iconic rink at Rockefeller Center and the Bank of America Winter Village at Bryant Park are bursting with holiday cheer (and fab food and drinks), while low-key rinks at NYC parks offer a more chill experience.', 'January 2024', 'Citywide','Outdoor Event',false,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1584201041506-b8f03a2c49fd?q=80&w=1475&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D','https://www.nycgovparks.org/facilities/iceskating'),
('The Secret World of Elephants at AMNH ', 'Majestic, incredible elephants are getting the spotlight in a new exhibit at The American Museum of Natural History. The Secret World of Elephants showcases both modern and ancient elephants, offering visitors a chance to see a full-scale model of a woolly mammoth, learn about what elephants eat, touch an elephant''s tooth, listen to elephant calls and more. The exhibition is now open in the museum’s LeFrak Family Gallery. An additional ticket is required to visit the exhibit; museum members can visit for free.', 'Opened November 13th, 2023', 'Manhattan', 'Art Exhibt', false,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1578326626553-39f72c545b07?q=80&w=2598&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D', 'https://www.amnh.org/exhibitions/secret-world-elephants?utm_source=performance-max&utm_medium=native&utm_campaign=amnhelephants-perfmax&utm_content=families&sourcenumber=53589&gad_source=1&gclid=Cj0KCQjwwYSwBhDcARIsAOyL0fjWECxozEEi_6H6bxnf7EMMB04ouDNO1HEp93zZUtX4SZZ0USuEL8UaAk6fEALw_wcB&gclsrc=aw.ds' ),
('Virtual NYRR Resolution Race', 'Whether you are shooting for a personal best or just looking to get moving, the Virtual NYRR Resolution Run 5K Powered by Strava is your chance to start 2024 feeling strong, healthy, and accomplished. Ease into your #ResolveToRun resolution with a 5K race you can run anywhere, anytime from January 1 through 7. You will be racing alongside thousands of other runners in our global NYRR Virtual Racing Powered by Strava community, so you’re sure to stay motivated.','January 1 - 8, 2024','Citywide','Marathon',true,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1483721310020-03333e577078?q=80&w=1528&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D', 'https://www.nyrr.org/races/virtualnyrrresolutionrun5k'),
('NYRR Joe Kleinerman 10k', 'The 2024 racing season begins at the NYRR Joe Kleinerman 10K this January. Recommit to running for your New Year''s resolution with a lap around Central Park—you''re almost guaranteed to set a season''s best! This race honors the late Joe Kleinerman (1912–2003), distance runner, track coach, and a founding member of NYRR.','January 6, 2024', 'Manhattan','Marathon',false,'https://prodsitecore.blob.core.windows.net/nyrrsitecoreblob/nyrr/image/photogallery/2024/joe-kleinerman-10k-gallery/004_joek24_sameday_dpl_025.jpg','https://www.nyrr.org/races/nyrrjoekleinerman10k'),
