('NYRR Brooklyn Bridge Walk Partnership with NYC DOT','Join us on Saturday, February 3, for the NYRR Brooklyn Bridge Walk in Partnership with NYC DOT, a free community one-mile walk on the iconic Brooklyn Bridge. The special event aims to highlight the decades-long collaboration between NYRR and the NYC Department of Transportation while giving community members the opportunity to enjoy an active morning to', 'Feburary 3, 2024', 'Brooklyn', 'Outdoor Event', true,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1625182918997-7f03991c6032?q=80&w=1472&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D','https://www.nyrr.org/races/nyrrbrooklynbridgewalkinpartnershipwithnycdot'),
('NYRR Manhattan 10K', 'Take a tour of Central Park by running the entire Ted Corbitt Loop at the NYRR Manhattan 10K. Yes, all the park''s beautiful hills are included! Harlem Hill, the Three Sisters, and Cat Hill are all yours to climb up and coast down on Sunday, February 4','February 4, 2024','Manhattan','Marathon',false,'https://prodsitecore.blob.core.windows.net/nyrrsitecoreblob/nyrr/image/photogallery/2024/manhattan-10k-gallery/05_manhattan10k-24_sameday_cgt_107.jpg','https://www.nyrr.org/races/nyrrmanhattan10k'),
('Losar Fest', 'This is our first LOSAR event since the pandemic. We are so excited to announce this FREE event on Feb 18th, 2023. An all-day celebration like you have never seen before. NYTSC students have prepared beautiful performances in Tibetan and English and win prizes from our $5 raffle tickets. Join us this lunar new year to learn about the Tibetan new year, check out the LOSAR market, grab a bite, and have a wonderful time!', 'february 18, 2024','Queens','Holiday Event','true','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526016650454-68a6f488910a?q=80&w=1548&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D','https://www.nytsc.org/events-2/losar-fest'),
('Winter''s Restaurant Week', 'With over 600 restaurants participating, this year’s selections for Restaurant Week has improved from prior years, with many classics as well as exciting new places represented. It starts today and runs through February 4, with eateries offering lunch or dinner specials, or both.','January 16 - February 4, 2024','Citywide','Food Event', false ,'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1414235077428-338989a2e8c0?q=80&w=1470&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D','https://www.nyctourism.com/restaurant-week/'),
